Each test case compares EL's structured output against independently verifiable
ground truth derived from the data — the same ground truth any LLM/RAG system
would need to get right to claim reliability.

Dataset: WA_Fn-UseC_-Telco-Customer-Churn.csv
Source: Kaggle blastchar/telco-customer-churn
